cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.PL, cs.SI. 

This paper focuses on software engineering and machine learning techniques to recommend mappings between methods from different libraries. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category. The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper deals with programming languages and APIs, which could place it in cs.PL (Programming Languages) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
